  "title": "WELDER",
  "description": "<p>Prepare and set up tools and equipment needed for welding tasks</p><p>Maintain a safe and secure work environment by following standard procedures</p><p>Ensure high quality work standards are met</p><p>Care and safely handle welding equipment and tools</p><p>Report fabrication issues and assist to resolve them as required</p><p>Report job related issues to supervisor</p><p>Inspect and maintain tools and welding equipment to ensure safe work environment</p><p>Document any safety incidents or hazards observed during operations</p><p>Perform other duties as assigned by supervisor</p><p>Skilled in gas cutting, PP welding, metal arc welding and orbital welding</p><p>Skilled in 3G, 4G, 5G, 6G welding techniques</p><p>Welding certification is an advantage</p><p>Able to follow standing SOPs and complete tasks within deadlines</p><p>Able to carry out heavy lifting, climbing and prolong stand</p>",
